@dc:title "Sierra bundle"
@dc:description "A packaging bundle that includes all Sierra vocabularies for operational analysis."
vocabulary bundle <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/bundle#> as v-bundle {
    includes <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> as dc
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/base#>
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/mission#>
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/entity#>
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/process#>
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/stakeholder#>
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/scenario#>
    includes <https://www.modelware.io/sierra/state#>
}
